			// main content 
			.content-main
				h1 Business details required by the IRS
				p
					| This information is required by the IRS on the EIN application. To save you time, weâ€™ve preselected the most common answers.
				h3
					| Will your business own a vehicle that weighs more than 55,000 pounds and is designed to transport loads on the highway?
				.form-group
					.form-fields
						input#irs1_01(name='irs1', type='radio')
						label(for='irs1_01') Yes
					.form-fields
						input#irs1_02(checked='checked', name='irs1', type='radio')
						label(for='irs1_02') No
					a#help_irs1_answer.help.icon.lz-icon-help.orange.small.desc
						| How did most people answer this question?
				h3
					| Will your business operate a casino or otherwise be involved with gambling or wagering?
				.form-group
					.form-fields
						input#irs2_01(name='irs2', type='radio')
						label(for='irs2_01') Yes
					.form-fields
						input#irs2_02(checked='checked', name='irs2', type='radio')
						label(for='irs2_02') No
					a#help_irs2_answer.help.icon.lz-icon-help.orange.small.desc
						| How did most people answer this question?
				h3 Will your business make or sell alcohol, tobacco or firearms?
				.form-group
					.form-fields
						input#irs3_01(name='irs3', type='radio')
						label(for='irs3_01') Yes
					.form-fields
						input#irs3_02(checked='checked', name='irs3', type='radio')
						label(for='irs3_02') No
					a#help_irs3_answer.help.icon.lz-icon-help.orange.small.desc
						| How did most people answer this question?
				h3 Will your business sell goods subject to an excise tax?
				p.tight
					| This is not common. Goods subject to excise tax include items such as fuel, tires, and fishing equipment. To see the full list of goods subject to this tax, 
					a#help_irs4.help click here
					| .
				.form-group
					.form-fields
						input#irs4_01(name='irs4', type='radio')
						label(for='irs4_01') Yes
					.form-fields
						input#irs4_02(checked='checked', name='irs4', type='radio')
						label(for='irs4_02') No
					a#help_irs4_answer.help.icon.lz-icon-help.orange.small.desc
						| How did most people answer this question?
				
